
Use the following command check out the latest source code:

svn checkout http://detour.googlecode.com/svn/branches/e17

Detour has 4 build-time options available. Look at main.edc:12

#define USE_ANIMATED_CURSOR (0/1)
This options sets whether or not you want the cursor to pulsate

#define USE_TANGO_ICONS (0/1)
You have the choice of using the default e17 icons or Tango icons

#define FADE_BAR_ICONS (0/1)
This options sets whether or not you want the icons of the ibar/ibox to fade

#define SEE_CONTEXT_MENUTITLE (0/1)
This options enables the context menu title

COMPILING and INSTALLING:

make

